snippet.title: The Chaput's Baby - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Chaput church was a well know place by the neighbors. Year gave way to year and the small church now is only the place where the Chaput family lives. Samantha is hired by the family to look after their baby, but things starts to go off inside that house.

BUY NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2118910/The_Chaputs_Baby/
